cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Indaga-agent, please cite it using the metadata in this file."
title: "Indaga-agent"
type: software
authors:
  - name: "birinets"
abstract: >-
  Local-first, multi-omic personal-health agent runtime (MCP): turns a consumer
  DNA chip and other health data into a queryable, honest expert — chip to
  imputation to annotation, behind one evidence-envelope honesty contract. Runs
  fully on-device; no personal data leaves the machine.
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-19"
license: "AGPL-3.0-or-later"
repository-code: "https://github.com/birinets/indaga-agent"
keywords:
  - genomics
  - multi-omic
  - personal health
  - MCP
  - local-first
  - evidence grounding
  - imputation
  - pharmacogenomics
  - polygenic scores
